S'Watch thousands of XFINITY On Demand\xe2\x84\xa2 TV Shows & Movies anytime, anywhere.Plus, now you can download thousands of hit shows & movies from Showtime, Starz, Encore and more to your Android tablet or phone & watch them anytime, anywhere -- even when you\xe2\x80\x99re offline.With the XFINITY TV Player app, you can watch thousands of hours of TV shows and movies.\xe2\x80\xa2 Watch content anytime, anywhere on any Wi-Fi connected Android Phone or Tablet\xe2\x80\xa2 Stream TV Shows and movies from your favorite networks, including premium channels like HBO, Starz, Showtime, Cinemax and cable channels like TNT, TBS, Cartoon Network and BBC America.\xe2\x80\xa2 Download TV shows & movies from Showtime, Starz, Encore and MoviePlex and watch them when you\xe2\x80\x99re offline.\xe2\x80\xa2 Set parental controls, so you can enjoy your content with privacy and peace of mind.REQUIREMENTS: \xe2\x80\xa2  Wi-Fi internet connection for streaming and download of video\xe2\x80\xa2 Android phone or tablet running Android 2.3 and higher.\xe2\x80\xa2 XFINITY TV or Comcast Digital Video service. You will also need a subscription to   one or more eligible channels to play content. \xe2\x80\xa2 Comcast ID or Comcast.net email address and password. Streaming and downloading of video is not available internationally.SUPPORT:Get Help Signing-In!\xe2\x80\xa2 Create a Comcast ID  --> https://login.comcast.net/myaccount/create-uid\xe2\x80\xa2 Look up your Comcast ID --> https://login.comcast.net/myaccount/lookup\xe2\x80\xa2 Retrieve your Comcast ID Password --> https://login.comcast.net/myaccount/reset*** Follow @XfinityTVApps on Twitter for tips and product information relating to all XFINITY mobile apps. **** Having trouble with the XFINITY TV Player App? Contact our support team via email: xfinity_remote@cable.comcast.com. We cannot respond through the Android Market comment/ratings system but would love to hear from you.**** Explanation of permissions requested:* permission.CALL_PHONE - Allows us to pass our support phone number to your dialer.* permission.INTERNET - Access the Internet.* permission.READ_PHONE_STATE - We use the ID of your phone to prevent playback abuse.* permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE - We tune playback if you are on WiFi.* permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE - We detect connectivity before allowing playback.* permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE - We cache browse images to your sdcard to save your bandwidth.* permission.WAKE_LOCK - We prevent your device from sleeping during playback.Recent changes:This update contains stability improvements, bug fixes, and improvements to screen layouts on several devices.'
